## ‚ú® **Why Choose Favorite Files Pro?**

Transform your Unreal Engine workflow with lightning-fast access to your most-used files. Whether you're a solo developer or part of a large team, Favorite Files Pro provides the professional file management tools you need to stay organized and productive.

### üéØ **Key Features**

- **üöÄ Lightning Fast Access** - Instant file opening with zero lag
- **üìÅ Smart Categorization** - Organize files by type, project, or custom categories
- **üé® Professional UI** - Beautiful, modern interface that integrates seamlessly
- **‚ö° Performance Optimized** - Preloaded file info for instant response
- **üîÑ Universal Compatibility** - Works with ANY file type, not just UE assets
